    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You have to see this beauty in person! It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it still looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve taken obsessed-level care of it, so it\u2019s in truly pristine, flawless shape. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new and ready for a smooth adventure, this is the one! Shoot me a message\u2014I\u2019d love to show it to you!",
      "price": 44500.0,
