    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This AP2-generation specimen represents the pinnacle of atmospheric engineering. Powered by the longitudinal F22C1 inline-four, the valvetrain remains in factory-spec clearance, delivering a linear power band to an 8,000 RPM redline. The close-ratio six-speed manual gearbox features precise gate engagement with no synchro drag, feeding power through a Torsen limited-slip differential. The chassis is anchored by a rigid X-bone frame and double-wishbone suspension at all four corners, with all bushings and ball joints exhibiting zero play. This is a collector-quality example with all original factory VIN tags present on every panel, offering a pure, unadulterated mechanical connection.",
